hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
1530,"Hazrat Saulbaa bin Zahdam sey riwayat hai ke hum tabristaan mein Hazrat Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath they aur hamarey sath Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Hazrat Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tum mein sey kisi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath salaate khof (khof ki namaz ) padhi hai? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey, phir unhoney aap ki namaz ka tariqa bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze khof eik giroh ko, jisney aap key peechhey saf baandhi thi, eik rakat padhaai aur doosra giroh aap key aur dushman key darmiyan tha (taake dushman namaz ki haalat mein hamla na kar sakey). to aap ney us giroh ko jo aap key peechhey tha, eik rakat padhaai, phir ye giroh dusrey giroh ki ladaai ki jagah mein pahunch gaya aur wo giroh un ki jagah aa gaya. aap ney in ko bhi eik rakat padhaai."
1531,"Hazrat Saulba bin Zahdam bayan kartey hain ke hum Saeed bin Aas key sath tabristaan mein (jihad kar rahey) they. unhoney kaha : tum mein sey kis ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaze khof padhi hai? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey, phir Hazrat Huzefa uthey aur logon ki do safein banaeen. eik saf apney peechhey aur dusri saf dushman key muqabil. apney peechhey wali saf ko aap ney eik rakat padhaai, phir ye un ki jagah chaley gaey aur wo (aap key peechhey) aa gaey. aap ney in ko bhi eik rakat padhaai, phir unhoney dusri rakat nahin padhi."
1532,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaz jaisi riwayat bayan ki hai.
1533,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Allah Taala ney tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani ghar ki namaz chaar rakat, safar ki namaz do rakat aur khof ki namaz eik rakat farz ki hai."
1534,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqam zoo-qird mein namaz (khof) padhi. logon ney aap key peechhey do safein banaeen. eik saf aap key peechhey aur eik saf dushman key muqabil, phir aap ney apney peechhey wali saf ko eik rakat padhaai, phir ye un ki jagah chaley gaey aur wo aa gaey. aap ney in ko bhi eik rakat padhaai. logon ney phir dusri rakat nahin padhi."
1535,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (namaz key liye) khadey huye aur log bhi aap key sath khadey huye. aap ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur logon ney bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kaha, phir aap ney rukoo farmaya aur un mein sey kuchh logon (pehli saff) ney sath rukoo kiya, phir aap ney sajda kiya aur unhoney bhi sajda kiya, phir aap dusri rakat key liye khadey huye to jinhoney aap key sath sajda kiya tha, wo peechhey hat kar apney sathiyon ki hifazat karney lagey aur doosra giroh aa gaya (pichhli saf aagey aa qaee). ab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (dusri rakat ka) rukoo aur sajdey kiye aur sab log namaz mein they aur takbeerein kehtey they lekin eik dusrey ki hifazat bhi kartey they."
1536,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke namaze-khof sirf do rakatein hai jaisey aaj kal tumharey (Hukkaam key) muhafiz tumharey imaamon key peechhey namaz padhtey hain, magar wo baari baari sajdey kartey they. (is tarah ke) un mein sey eik giroh khada rehta, halanke wo sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hi key sath khadey hotey they aur eik giroh key log (agli saf waley) aap key sath sajdey kartey they, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey hotey aur wo sab aap key sath khadey ho jatey, phir aap rukoo farmatey aur wo sab aap key sath rukoo mein jatey, phir aap sajda kartey to aap key sath wo log sajda kartey jo pehli rakat mein khadey rahey they, phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath sajda karney waley namaz key aakhir mein bethtey to jo log khadey rahey they, unhoney apney taur par sajdey kiye, phir wo bhi beth gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik hi waqt) un sab key sath salam pheraa."
1537,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abu-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaze khof (is tarah) padhaai (ke) aap ney eik saf apney peechhey khadi kar li aur dusri saf dushman key muqabil khadi rahi. aap ney apney peechhey wali saf ko eik rakat padhaai, phir ye (dushman key muqabley mein) chaley gaey aur wo dusrey aa gaey. aap ney in ko bhi eik rakat padhaai, phir wo uthey aur un sab (dono girohon) ney eik eik rakat apney taur par padh li."
1538,"Hazrat Saleh bin Khuwaat ney us sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya jisney ghazwae-zaaturriqaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaze khof padhi thi ke eik giroh ney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey saf bandi ki aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabley mein raha. aap ney apney sath waley logon ko eik rakat padhaai, phir aap khadey rahey aur unhoney apni dusri rakat padh li, phir wo chaley gaey aur dushman key muqabley mein saf bandi kar li aur doosra giroh aap key peechhey aa gaya. aap ney unhein baqi bachi hui (dusri) rakat padha di, phir aap bethey rahey aur unhoney apni dusri rakat mukammal kar li, phir aap ney unkey sath salam pheraa."
1539,"Hazrat Salim apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma) sey bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik giroh ko eik rakat padhaai jabkey doosra giroh dushman key bilmuqaabil tha, phir ye (pehla giroh) un ki jagah chala gaya aur wo aa gaey. aap ney in ko dusri rakat padha di, phir aap ney salam pher diya, phir ye khadey huye aur apni dusri rakat padhi, phir wo khadey huye aur unhoney apni dusri rakat apney taur par padh li."
1540,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Najad ki taraf jang key liye gaya. wahan hamara dushman sey samna huwa to hamney unkey muqabley mein safein baandh len. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz padhaai to hum mein sey eik giroh aap key peechhey khada ho gaya aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabley mein raha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney peechhey khadey honey waley giroh key sath eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye, phir wo un logon (dusrey giroh) ki jagah ja kar khadey ho gaey jinhoney namaz na padhi thi aur wo giroh aa gaya jinhoney namaz na padhi thi. aap ney unkey sath bhi eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye (yani unkey sath bhi eik rakat ada ki).  phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam pher diya, phir musalmanon mein sey har aadmi utha aur us ney apney taur par eik rukoo aur do sajdey kar liye (yani eik eik rakat padh li)."
1541,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma farmatey they ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaze khof padhi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha. hum mein sey eik giroh ney aap key peechhey saf bandi ki aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabil raha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pehley giroh key sath eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye (yani eik rakat padhaai), phir wo chaley gaey aur dushman key muqabil saf aaraa ho gaey aur doosra giroh aap key peechhey khada ho gaya aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz shuru kar di. aap ney isi tarah kiya (yani in ko bhi eik rakat padhaai). phir aap ney salam pher diya, phir dono girohon mein sey har shakhs utha aur us ney apney taur par eik rukoo aur do sajdey kar liye (yani eik eik rakat padh li)."
1542,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze khof padhaai. aap khadey huye aur (Allahu-Akbar) kaha to hum mein sey eik giroh aap key peechhey namaz padhney laga aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabil raha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey sath eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye, phir wo salam pherey baghair chaley gaey aur dusron ki jagah dushman key samney khadey ho gaey, phir dusrey giroh ney aa kar aap key peechhey saf bandi ki. aap ney unkey sath bhi eik rukoo aur do sajdey kiye, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam pher diya jabkey aap do rukoo aur chaar sajdey (yani do rakatein) mukammal farma chukey they, phir dono giroh uthey aur un mein sey har shakhs ney apney apney taur par eik rukoo aur do sajdey kar liye. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key shagrid) Abu-Bakar bin Suni bayan kartey hain ke Imam Zohri ney Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey sirf do hadeesein suni hain lekin ye riwayat un mein shamil nahin (goya is riwayat ki sanad mein taaluq khatm ho)."
1543,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi jang key dino mein namaze khof padhaai to eik giroh aap key peechhey khada ho gaya aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabil khada raha. aap ney apney sath walon ko eik rakat padha di, phir wo chaley gaey aur dusrey aa gaey. aap ney in ko bhi eik rakat padha di, phir dono girohon ney eik eik rakat apney taurr par padh li."
1544,"Hazrat Marwan bin Hakam ney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaze khof padhi hai? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : kab? aap ney farmaya : ghazwaey-najad key saal. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki namaz key liye uthey aur eik giroh bhi aap key sath khada huwa jabkey doosra giroh dushman key muqabil tha aur un ki pusht qibley ki taraf thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha to sab musalmanon ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha (yani namaz shuru kar li) aap key sath walon ney bhi aur unhoney bhi jo dushman key muqabil they, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney rukoo farmaya to aap key sath waley giroh ney bhi rukoo kiya, phir aap ney sajda farmaya to aap key sath waley giroh ney bhi sajda kiya jab ke dusrey giroh waley dushman key muqabil khadey rahey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huye to aap key sath waley bhi uth khadey huye aur wo dushman ki taraf ja kar unkey muqabil khadey ho gaey aur jo pehley dushman key muqabil they unhoney aap key peechhey aa kar apna rukoo aur sujood kiya (yani eik rakat apney taur par padh li). us doran mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah khadey rahey (jis tarah aap khadey they). phir wo khadey huye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dusri rakat ka rukoo farmaya unhoney bhi aap key sath rukoo kiya, phir aap ney sajda farmaya to unhoney bhi aap key sath sajdey kiye, phir wo giroh bhi aa gaya jo dushman key muqabil tha. unhoney (apney taur par) rukoo aur sujood kiye (yani apni baqiiya rakat padh li). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath waley is doran mein bethey rahey. phir salam ka waqt aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam pher diya aur sab (dono girohon) ney salam pher diya, is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki do rakaten ho gaeen aur dono girohon mein sey har eik ki bhi do rakaten ho gaeen."
1545,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zajnaan aur Asfan phaad key darmiyan qiyam farma they aur mushrekin ka muhaasra kiye huye they. mushrikon ney kaha (program banaya) ke in musalmanon ki eik namaz aisi hai (namaze Asr) jo inhein apney nojawan beton aur betiyon sey bhi ziyada piyari hai to tum baat tey kar lo (pukhta program bana lo) aur (us namaz key doran mein) un par yakbaargi hamla kar do. udhar sey Hazrat Jibril alehissalam tashrif laye aur aap ko hukm diya ke aap apney sahaba key do giroh bana den. aap un mein sey eik giroh ko namaz padhaaen aur doosra giroh dushman ki taraf mutawajjeh rahey. wo mohtaat rahen aur apna aslaha pehney rahen. aap pehley giroh ko eik rakat padha den, phir wo peechhey hat jaeyn (aur dushman key muqabil chaley jaeyn) aur dusrey aa jaaeyn phir eik rakat aap in ko padha den to is tarah un ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik eik rakat ho jaeygi aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki do rakatein ho jaaeyngi."
1546,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaze khof padhaai. eik saf aap key aagey (dushman key muqabil) khadi ho gaee aur dusri aap key peechhey. aap ney apney peechhey khadey honey walon ko eik rukoo aur do sajdey, yani eik rakat padhaai, phir ye aagey chaley gaey aur apney sathiyon ki jagah khadey ho gaey aur wo aagey aur (aap key peechhey) un ki jagah khadey ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein bhi eik rukoo aur do sajdey, yani eik rakat padhaai, phir aap ney salam pher diya. is tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki do rakatein ho gaeen aur un ki eik eik."
1547,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (eik jang mein) they. namaz ki iqaamat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur musalmanon ka eik giroh bhi aap key peechhey khada ho gaya jabkey doosra giroh dushman key muqabil raha. aap ney apney peechhey khadey honey walon ko eik rukoo aur do sajdey, yani eik rakat padhaai, phir wo chaley gaey aur un logon ki jagah khadey ho gaey jo dushman key muqabley mein they aur wo doosra giroh aa gaya. aap ney unhein bhi eik rukoo aur do sajdey, yani eik rakat padhaai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam phera, aap key peechhey waley logon ney bhi aur dusron ney bhi salam pher diya."
1548,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaze khof mein hazir huye. hum aap key peechhey do safon mein khadey ho gaey. dushman hamarey aur qibley key darmiyan tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha, hum sab ney bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kaha phir aap ney rukoo kiya to hamney bhi rukoo kiya, phir aap ney sar uthaya to hamney bhi (rukoo sey) sar uthaya, phir jab aap sajdey key liye jhukey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sajda kiya aur un logon ney bhi jo aap key sath qaribi (pehli) saf mein they jabkey dusri saf waley khadey rahey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (sajdey sey) sar uthaya aur us saf walon ney jo aap key qarib thi to dusri saf ney apni jagah hi apney sajdey ada kiye, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath wali saf waley peechhey hat gaey aur dusri saf waley aagey ho kar pehli saf walon ki jagah khadey ho gaey aur wo un ki jagah khadey ho gaey, phir (dusri rakat mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney rukoo farmaya to hamney bhi aap key sath rukoo kiya, phir aap ney (rukoo sey) sar uthaya to hum sab ney bhi (rukoo sey) sar uthaya. jab aap sajdey key liye zamin ki taraf jhukey to aap key sath wali saf ney sajdey kiye aur dusri saf waley khadey rahey, phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath walon ney dono sajdon sey sar uthaey to pichhli saf walon ney apney taur par sajdey kar liye, phir aap ney (sab key sath eik hi waqt mein) salam pher diya."
1549,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum maqame nakhl (Madiney sey do raat key fasley par) mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they jabkey dushman hamarey aur qibley key darmiyan tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney takbire tahreema kahi to sab musalmanon ney takbire tahreema kahi, phir aap ney rukoo farmaya to un sab ney bhi rukoo kiya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath wali saf ney sajda kiya jabkey dusri saf waley khadey un ki hifazat kartey rahey, phir jab wo sajdon key baad uthey to pichhli saf walon ney apni jagah hi mein sajdey (mukammal) kar liye, phir ye un ki jagah chaley gaey (aur wo aa gaey). phir aap ney (dusri rakat ka) rukoo kiya to sab ney rukoo kiya. phir aap ney sar uthaya to un sab ney bhi apney sar uthaey, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath wali saf ney sajda kiya aur dusrey khadey un ki hifazat kartey rahey. jab wo sajdon sey farigh ho kar beth gaey to pichhli saf walon ney apni jagah hi mein sajdey kar liye, phir aap ney salam pheraa. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jaisey tumharey Ameeron (key pehrey-daar) kartey hain."
1550,"Hazrat Abu Aaysh-Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Asfan key ilaqey mein dushman key sath jang ki haalat mein they. mushrekin key Ameer Khalid bin Waleed they (jo us waqt musalman nahin huye they). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ko Zohar ki namaz padhaai to mushrekin ney kaha : is namaz key baad eik aisi namaz hai (namaze Asr) jo in musalmanon ko apney maal-daulat aur aulad sey bhi ziyada piyari hai (lihaza us namaz mein in par hamla kar do). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ko Asr ki namaz is tarah padhaai ke apney peechhey un ki do safein bana lein, phir aap ney un sab key sath rukoo kiya, phir jab unhoney rukoo sey sar uthaya (aur aap sajdey mein gaey) to aap key sath wali (yani pehli) saf hi ney sajdey kiye aur dusri saf waley khadey rahey. jab unhoney sajdon sey sar uthaey to dusri saf ney sajdey kiye jabkey rukoo to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath kar chukey they, phir agli saf peechhey ho gaee aur pichhli aagey aur wo eik dusrey ki jagah mein khadey ho gaey. phir Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sab key sath rukoo kiya. jab unhoney rukoo sey sar uthaey to aap key sath sirf aap key sath wali saf ney sajdey kiye jabkey dusrey khadey rahey, phir jab wo apney sajdon sey farigh huye to pichhli saf walon ney (apney) sajdey ada kiye, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sab key sath eik hi waqt  mein salam pheraa."
1551,"Hazrat Abu Ayaash Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Asfan key maqam par they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein Zohar ki namaz padhaai. un dino mushrekin key Ameer Khalid bin Waleed they. mushrekin ney kaha : afsos ! hamney unhein ghafil paya tha. (kash hum hamla kar detey) to Zohar aur Asr key darmiyan namaze khof ka hukm utra. hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is tarah Asr ki namaz padhaai ke hamarey do giroh bana diye. eik giroh Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhta tha aur doosra giroh un ki hifazat karta tha. aap ney sab key sath takbir kahi, jo aap key sath they aur jo un ki hifazat kartey they, phir aap ney rukoo farmaya to dono girohon ney rukoo kiya, phir aap key sath waley giroh ney sajdey kiye, phir sath waley peechhey hat aaye aur dusrey aagey badhey aur unhoney apney sajdey mukammal kiye, phir aap (dusri rakat key liye) uthey aur sab key sath rukoo kiya, jo aap key sath they aur jo un ki hifazat kartey they, phir aap ney apney sath walon key sath sajdey kiye, phir wo peechhey hat gaey aur apney dusrey sathiyon ki jagah mein khadey ho gaey aur dusrey aagey badhey aur unhoney apney sajdey purey kiye, phir aap ney sab key sath salam pheraa. is tarah un mein sey har eik ki apney Imam key sath do do rakaten ho gaeen, aur eik dafa aap ney banu Sulaim key ilaqey mein bhi namaze khof padhi thi."
1552,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik giroh ko namaze-khof do rakat padhaai, phir salam pher diya, phir dusrey giroh ko do rakaten padhaeen aur phir salam pher diya. is tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar rakaat padhin."
1553,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba mein sey eik giroh ko do rakaten padhaain, phir salam phera, phir dusrey giroh ko bhi do rakaten padhaain, phir salam pheraa."
1554,"Hazrat Sahal bin Abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey namaze khof key barey mein riwayat hai ke Imam qibla rukh khada ho, aur muqtadiyon mein sey eik giroh uskey sath khada ho jaey aur doosra giroh dushman key muqabil un ki taraf munh kar key khada rahey. to Imam pehley giroh ko eik rakat padha dey, phir wo apni jagah khadey ho kar dusri rakat key rukoo sajdey ada kar lein. aur dusron ki jagah chaley jaeyn aur wo aa jaeyn to Imam unhein bhi rukoo aur do sajdey padha dey. is tarah Imam ki do rakatein ho jaeyngi aur un ki eik rakat, phir wo khud dusri rakat key rukoo aur do sajdey ada kar len."
1555,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba ko namaze khof padhaai. un mein sey eik giroh ney aap key sath namaz padhi aur dusrey giroh key chehrey dushman ki taraf they. to aap ney eik giroh ko do rakat padha din, phir wo dusrey giroh ki jagah chaley gaey aur dusrey aa gaey. aap ney unhein bhi do rakaten padhaain aur salam pher diya."
1556,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney peechhey khadey logon ko do rakaten padhaain, phir jo unkey baad aaye, unhein bhi do rakaten padhaain. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki chaar rakaten ho gaeen aur un ki do do."
